description._content: Description: 5. Typical scene in northern range forests. Derelict forest cleared by excessive cutting and grazing. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: 6. Typical scene in northern range forests. Steep slope cleared of excessive cutting and grazing and now degenerating still further. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
